div.p:
Finally, that the arbitrator shall fix the amount of the indemnity which may
                        be due from the Russian Government on account of the claims presented by the
                        parties in interest;

Whereas the defendant party admits as justified the claims for provisions
                        consumed, $200; for lodgings for the crew, $210; for personal expenses of
                        Captain Scullun, $50; total, $460;
